## Key Implementation
- Use FlatList instead of ScrollView for efficient virtualized rendering with large datasets
- Implement keyExtractor for stable item identification and optimal diffing
- Add getItemLayout to enable smooth scrolling by providing item dimensions upfront
- Configure initialNumToRender and maxToRenderPerBatch to balance performance and user experience

## Performance Optimizations
- Memoize renderItem components with React.memo to prevent unnecessary re-renders
- Use windowSize prop to control the render window and reduce memory footprint
- Implement image caching with react-native-fast-image for efficient image loading
- Consider removeClippedSubviews for memory optimization with complex lists
- Optimize data structure to minimize update calculations

